       01  XIJICOMM-CA.
           COPY  XIJICOMM.
      *   조회DC  INTERFACE
       01  XDJL4111-CA.
           COPY  XDJL4111.
130816*   처리DC  INTERFACE
       01  XDJLB111-CA.
           COPY  XDJLB111.
      *   출력영역확보　및　초기화INTERFACE
       01  XZUGOTMY-CA.
           COPY  XZUGOTMY.
